snippet.title: The Accountant Intervenes By Driving Through A Police Blockade | Drive Angry
snippet.description:
The Accountant (William Fichtner) intervenes when John (Nicolas Cage) and Piper (Amber Heard) are stopped by the police, and drives a truck full of hydrogen right into them. 

#AllOutAction #DriveAngry
